Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.basic

Class AbstractScriptEngineFactory

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.basic.AbstractScriptEngineFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
AsmScriptEngineFactory
public abstract class AbstractScriptEngineFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory

This class implements basic functionality for the ScriptEngineFactory interface. It's functionality is oriented to use with the AbstractScriptEngine class in this package. The good examples of the child implementation for the given class is AsmScriptEngineFactory class in this package. All children, that extends this class, must register them as an SPI service. File to register is META-INF/services/javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory

This class is not thread-safe.

Since:
0.0.2
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
ScriptEngineFactory, AsmScriptEngineFactory, JUnit tests
LastUpdate:
0.0.3
